Building Computer vision based application that can analyze trend and provide insights looking at candlestick patterns of stock or any financial ticker 

Why?
1. Price action trading and other trading strategies like Mean reversion, Trend following etc. requires understanding of Candlestick patterns


Tech:
1. Heroku for deployement
2. Streamlit for Front end and prototype
3. Some LLM stack for generating insights on pattern
4. OpenCV for image to text
